ygData.messageBody:
Hello, everyone-

My name is Christine and I've been lurking on the list for about a week or so
now. Thought I'd introduce myself and indicate my interest in the guild
formation happening this evening. I do plan on being in the chat room about
7:30 p.m. MDT (here in toasty Denver).

I'm a lesbian (age 43) who has been playing EQ for about a month now. I have
two characters on Brell, one on Quellious and two on Erollisi Marr. They are
as follows:

Brell Serillis Server:

Ananda, gnome cleric of Brell, 5th level, beginning tailoring and smithing
skills (sharpen those rusty weapons!)

Mirri, wood elf druid of Tunare, 4th level, beginning tailoring skills

Quellious Server:

Ariale, erudin wizard of Quellious, 5th level

Erollisi Marr Server:

Sharada, high-elf cleric of Tunare, 8th level
Minbari, high-elf enchanter, 6th level, beginning jewelry skills

My partner, Danielle, will be playing EQ as soon as we get our DSL installed
and the new computers up (new vid cards, etc.), sometime in the next month. We
are both looking forward to making some new friends and adventuring to parts
unknown.

See you in chat this evening.

Christine
ChrisRAV4@...
